@baseUrl = http://localhost:3001

### PENTING: Untuk mendapatkan token verifikasi yang valid:
# 1. Jalankan request di file 'get-verification-token.http' untuk mendaftar user baru
# 2. Salin nilai tokenId dan token dari respons registration
# 3. Gunakan nilai tersebut di request di bawah ini

### Verify email via POST (body)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/verify-email
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "tokenId": "cmeyblo9600032v4tqol6bhcn",
  "token": "ddee159da17b3213d44052f67641afad37bf8fcfcc573716"
}

### Verify email via GET link (query params)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/verify-email?tokenId=your_token_id_here&token=your_verification_token_here

### Verify with invalid token (should fail with 400)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/verify-email
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "tokenId": "invalid_id",
  "token": "invalid_token"
}

### Verify with missing fields (should fail with 400)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/verify-email
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "tokenId": "some_id"
}